Usage: Hyde-tool [Function] [options]

 
[man]                       ﬌ Show Manual

 
[zoom]                      ﬌ Zoom in/out Hyprland

			 [in]  ﬌ Zoom in

			 [out]  ﬌ Zoom out

			 [reset]  ﬌ Reset Zoom
====================================================================================================================================

